    "en": "Question words are used to ask for information. At A1 level, the most basic question words are introduced.\n\n<strong>1. Basic Question Words</strong>\n- Wer? (Who?)\n- Was? (What?)\n- Wo? (Where?)\n- Wann? (When?)\n- Warum? (Why?)\n- Wie? (How?)\n- Wie viel? (How much?)\n\n<strong>2. Sentence Structure</strong>\nQuestion word + Verb + Subject + Other elements\n- Wer bist du? (Who are you?)\n- Wo wohnst du? (Where do you live?)\n\n<strong>3. Summary</strong>\nQuestion words are essential to get information in daily communication.",
    
